---
---

<header id="hero" class="pt-14 sm:pt-20 pb-12 sm:pb-16 border-b border-ink-100">
  <div class="hero-container">
    <div>
      <div>
        <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <span class="label">ERC-8211</span>
          <span class="label">Standards Track</span>
          <span class="label">Draft</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5.5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 max-w-2xl">
          ERC-8211: Smart Batching
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-ink-500 font-display italic max-w-xl leading-snug mb-8">
          From transactions to programs.
        </p>

        <div class="prose-body max-w-xl mb-10">
          <p>
            A batch encoding where each parameter declares <em>how to obtain its value</em> at
            execution time and <em>what conditions that value must satisfy</em>. No Solidity required.
            No contract deployment. No audit cycles for new flows.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <a
            href="https://t.me/smartbatching"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#229ED9] text-white font-medium text-base shadow-sm hover:bg-[#1b8cc2] hover:shadow-md transition-all"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M9.78 18.65l.28-4.23 7.68-6.92c.34-.31-.07-.46-.52-.19L7.74 13.3 3.64 12c-.88-.25-.89-.86.2-1.3l15.97-6.16c.73-.33 1.43.18 1.15 1.3l-2.72 12.81c-.19.91-.74 1.13-1.5.71L12.6 16.3l-1.99 1.93c-.23.23-.42.42-.83.42z"/>
            </svg>
            Join the Telegram group
            <span class="text-white/80 text-sm font-normal">@smartbatching</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-70 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm flex-wrap">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/ethereum/ERCs/pull/1638"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-accent hover:underline font-medium"
          >
            Full specification
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <span class="text-ink-200">|</span>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/bcnmy/composable-batch-erc"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-ink-500 hover:text-ink-900 transition-colors"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>
          <span class="text-ink-200">|</span>
          <a
            href="https://ethereum-magicians.org/t/erc-8211-smart-batching/28135"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-ink-500 hover:text-ink-900 transition-colors"
          >
            Discussion
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-ink-100 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs text-ink-400">
      <div>
        <span class="text-ink-300">Authors</span>&ensp;
        <a href="https://github.com/oxshaman" class="hover:text-accent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mislav Javor</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/fichiokaku" class="hover:text-accent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Filip Dujmušić</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/filmakarov" class="hover:text-accent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Filipp Makarov</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/vr16x" class="hover:text-accent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Venkatesh Rajendran</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="text-ink-300">Created</span>&ensp;2026-02-11
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
